Common Tasks
Add a New Section
In app/page.tsx, add before the footer:
<section className="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
  <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Your Section</h2>
    {/* Your content */}
  </div>
</section>
Change Logo
Find this code (~line 125):
<div className="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f766e] to-[#14b8a6] rounded-lg">
  D&G
</div>
Replace with an <img> tag or your custom logo component.
Add Analytics
In app/layout.tsx, add before closing </body>:
<Script
  src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=YOUR_ID"
  strategy="afterInteractive"
/>
